297
00:23:50,862 --> 00:23:51,895
Liza, I'm sorry.

298
00:23:51,897 --> 00:23:53,131
Shh, shh, shh.

299
00:24:00,038 --> 00:24:01,372
Holy shit.

300
00:24:03,374 --> 00:24:05,542
