He's getting his anger out.

362
00:30:14,846 --> 00:30:16,415
It's pretty violent.

363
00:31:25,417 --> 00:31:26,652
Really?

364
00:31:33,692 --> 00:31:35,291
That wasn't funny.

365
00:31:35,293 --> 00:31:37,293
You're supposed
to stay in this room

366
00:31:37,295 --> 00:31:39,797
and not come out again until
you're ready to apologize.

367
00:31:48,172 --> 00:31:50,875
Fine. You can stay in here
for the rest of the day, then.

368
00:32:31,517 --> 00:32:32,418
Aaah!

369
00:33:13,224 --> 00:33:14,857
Jude,

370
00:33:14,859 --> 00:33:16,762
your father and I
said no doll.

371
00:33:19,297 --> 00:33:21,933
Okay, I am gonna count to three,
and if this door isn't open...

372
00:33:23,067 --> 00:33:24,367
One...

373
00:33:24,369 --> 00:33:25,736
two...

374
00:33:25,738 --> 00:33:26,638
three.

375
00:33:33,978 --> 00:33:35,814
What are you doing here?

376
00:34:05,243 --> 00:34:06,510
Hey.

377
00:34:06,512 --> 00:34:08,146
I have someone here
who wants to apologize.

378
00:34:09,914 --> 00:34:10,816
Come on.

379
00:34:13,317 --> 00:34:14,185
Hey.

380
00:34:27,031 --> 00:34:28,801
Thank you for apologizing.

381
00:34:35,474 --> 00:34:37,707
Okay. Let's get you
