390
00:35:06,370 --> 00:35:07,706
I don't know what to do.

391
00:35:09,675 --> 00:35:12,009
I just feel like
I'm letting you and Jude down.

392
00:35:13,144 --> 00:35:14,811
You're not
letting anyone down.

393
00:35:14,813 --> 00:35:17,213
Please don't be sorry.

394
00:35:17,215 --> 00:35:18,515
