424
00:37:45,631 --> 00:37:47,899
You've scrubbed up well,
little man.

425
00:37:51,168 --> 00:37:53,572
So, I see you've found
yourself a new family.

426
00:38:03,314 --> 00:38:05,050
How're you doing,
little fella?

427
00:38:11,657 --> 00:38:14,024
Just look at that expression
