428
00:38:14,026 --> 00:38:17,496
It's like he's got a secret
that only he knows.

429
00:38:19,531 --> 00:38:21,500
Do you ever notice that?

430
00:38:24,403 --> 00:38:25,869
Can I help you?

431
00:38:25,871 --> 00:38:27,070
Hello there.

432
00:38:27,072 --> 00:38:30,205
