It was just there.

443
00:40:56,855 --> 00:40:58,555
- I'm sorry.
- My God, Liza.

444
00:40:58,557 --> 00:40:59,257
What are you doing?

445
00:41:27,752 --> 00:41:29,187
Jude?

446
00:42:00,318 --> 00:42:02,988
